OL,3,CWater park's frustration after
OL,4,Cswimmers seen drinking and taking
OL,5,Cdrugs by lake
OL,7,FAn outdoor water park has criticised
OL,8,Fadults "risking their lives" after
OL,9,Fpeople were spotted drinking alcohol
OL,10,Fand taking drugs before swimming.
OL,12,FWelton Waters Activity Centre near
OL,13,FHull said staff had seen a number of
OL,14,Fadults smoking cannabis and even
OL,15,Finhaling nitrous oxide from balloons
OL,16,Fbefore taking a dip last week.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
