CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F331A1782746334
OL,3,CWater park's frustration after
OL,4,Cswimmers seen drinking and taking
OL,5,Cdrugs by lake
OL,7,FThe Centre, which offers wild swimming
OL,8,Fand kayaking, said the bathers were
OL,9,Fasked to leave the site after being
OL,10,Fseen taking substances on the water
OL,11,Fbanks.
OL,13,FEsther Pounds, an administrator for
OL,14,Fthe attraction, said it wasn't just
OL,15,Ftheir own lives they risked but also
OL,16,Fother staff and visitors.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,332,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F331A1782746334
OL,3,CWater park's frustration after
OL,4,Cswimmers seen drinking and taking
OL,5,Cdrugs by lake
OL,7,FShe told ITV News: "It should go
OL,8,Fwithout saying you cold drown. By
OL,9,Fdrinking or taking drugs before
OL,10,Fswimming, you're putting yourself in
OL,11,Freal danger, but you're also putting
OL,12,Fothers in danger too should they need
OL,13,Fto try and rescue you."
OL,15,F"We could see them smoking cannabis
OL,16,Fand inhaling nitrous oxide from
OL,17,Fballoons. They were warned against it
OL,18,Fand told the dangers of what they were
OL,19,Fdoing - I don't think it was taken
OL,20,Fkindly."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,332,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F331A1782746334
OL,3,CWater park's frustration after
OL,4,Cswimmers seen drinking and taking
OL,5,Cdrugs by lake
OL,7,FShe added: "People just do what they
OL,8,Fwant to do and don't listen to others.
OL,9,FThey pretty much think that they're
OL,10,Funtouchable or that the rules don't
OL,11,Fapply."
OL,13,FIt follows a number of incidents in
OL,14,Frecent weeks where a number of people
OL,15,F- including several children and young
OL,16,Fpeople - have lost their lives in
OL,17,Fincidents in the water.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
