FL,332,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F331A1782746334
OL,3,CWater park's frustration after
OL,4,Cswimmers seen drinking and taking
OL,5,Cdrugs by lake
OL,7,FOn Saturday evening, the body of a 15-
OL,8,Fyear-old boy was recovered from the
OL,9,Fwater at Cowbury Reservoir in
OL,10,FStalybridge, Greater Manchester, after
OL,11,Fhe was reported to have got into
OL,12,Fdifficulty.
OL,14,FLast month, 17 people were reported to
OL,15,Fhave died in water-related tragedies
OL,16,Fduring a spell of particularly warm
OL,17,Fweather.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
