FL,332,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F331A1782746334
OL,3,CWater park's frustration after
OL,4,Cswimmers seen drinking and taking
OL,5,Cdrugs by lake
OL,7,FAccording to the Royal Life Saving
OL,8,FSociety, 46% of accidental drownings
OL,9,Fin people aged 18 to 25 involve
OL,10,Falcohol or drugs.
OL,12,FThe organisation has reiterated safety
OL,13,Fmessages surrounding drinking and
OL,14,Fswimming, with alcohol being known to
OL,15,Flimit muscle ability, slowing reaction
OL,16,Ftimes and numbing the senses - all of
OL,17,Fwhich heighten the risk of drowning or
OL,18,Fcold water shock.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
